# Build artefacts — excluded from the docker context for faster builds
# and to avoid leaking host-specific paths into the image.
**/bin
**/obj
**/.vs
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/*.user

# Tests — not needed in the production image. The InternalsVisibleTo
# directive in the csproj is a build-time concern, not a file dep.
tests/

# Local secrets / settings that shouldn't ship.
**/*.user.json
**/secrets.json
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Misc
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/*.md
